title: (Mon Part 2) Bobby Did Something Last Night He Says He’d Never Do… + What Amy Screamed About Off-Air That We Had To Address
itunes:title: (Mon Part 2) Bobby Did Something Last Night He Says He’d Never Do… + What Amy Screamed About Off-Air That We Had To Address
description:
Bobby said at dinner last night he did something he said he would never say he’d do and hates himself for it. We play a game where Amy and Lunchbox try to identify the most famous rock song intros. They both don’t know a whole lot about music. Amy also made a request for the next time a certain country artist comes into the studio. We decided whether or not it will be awkward or not.
